        </div>

        <div class="testimonial">
            <h3>Sally Race</h3>
            <p>I studied at Perfect Fifth Studios for three years. Jackie was exactly what I was looking for.  I had been singing improperly for years but Jackie was the only teacher who really helped me understand how to properly use my voice.  As a result of coming to Perfect Fifth Studios my voice is healthier and stronger. Working with Jackie was so easy because she cares so much about her students.  She knows about all of her students extracurricular activities and helps you to schedule around them so that there’s always time for voice lessons.  Jackie is always prepared with songs from any particular musical and other songs that sounded good for my voice months before an audition so that I feel as prepared as possible. If you’re on the fence about working with Jackie I strongly recommend her!</p>
